    "body": "This is a high level ticket which encompasses several issues.\r\n\r\n* A general swarm metrics system for network testing and observability has been implemented with ticket https://github.com/ethersphere/go-ethereum/issues/183, using the `go-ethereum` metrics code\r\n* p2p accounting metrics have been implemented with PR https://github.com/ethersphere/go-ethereum/issues/845 and https://github.com/ethersphere/go-ethereum/issues/1005\r\n* There is an open ticket to document the p2p accounting metrics, which are user facing, here https://github.com/ethersphere/go-ethereum/issues/1036\r\n\r\nFor these reasons it is best to close this high level ticket. For further needs about metrics new tickets can be created",
